    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long cloaks, often with a wide, round collar, made of fur or lined or trimmed with fur and worn by men and women.  Also, similar cloaks made of cotton or silk and worn by women and children.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
